snippet.title: The Invisible Hand - Coming May 7 2021
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/628200/The_Invisible_Hand/
GOG: https://www.gog.com/game/the_invisible_hand
Humble: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/the-invisible-hand

Want to get rich, quick? Welcome to FERIOS, where you’ll be empowered to pursue wealth and success as a mid-level stockbroker! Your wildest dreams of wealth can come true… at the cost of everything else.
